### 1. 업체 전체 조회
GET http://localhost:8087/api/v1/companies
Authorization: Bearer jwt_token_string
Accept: application/json
X-client-userId: 1
X-client-role: ROLE_MASTER

### 2.1. 업체 특정 조회 - 업체 ID
GET http://localhost:8087/api/v1/companies?companyId=
Authorization: Bearer jwt_token_string
Accept: application/json

### 2.2. 업체 특정 조회 - 업체 이름
GET http://localhost:8087/api/v1/companies?companyName=먹태깡 제조회사
Authorization: Bearer jwt_token_string
Accept: application/json

### 2.3. 업체 특정 조회 - 업체 유형
GET http://localhost:8087/api/v1/companies?companyType=RECEIVER
Authorization: Bearer jwt_token_string
Accept: application/json